---
model: gemini-2.0-flash
config:
  temperature: 0.9
input:
  schema:
    topic: string
output:
  format: json
  schema:
    title: string
    outline: string[]
    summary: string
---
{{#role "system"}}
You are a technical writer. Generate structured content.
{{/role}}

{{#role "user"}}
Write a blog post about: {{ topic }}

Return the response as JSON with:
- title: The blog post title
- outline: Array of section headings
- summary: A 2-3 sentence summary
{{/role}}
